\par Born 1938, London. 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\ul\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\langfenp1033\insrsid2895163\charrsid2895163 Family}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
